text: Up the River is a 1930 American comedy movie directed by John Ford and starring Spencer Tracy, Clarice Luce, Humphrey Bogart, Warren Hymer, William Collier, Sr.. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox and was remade in 1938. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1930 comedy movies Category:American comedy movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by John Ford
title: Up the River
